msgid "Raster boolean AND"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2089
msgid ""
"Calculates the boolean ``AND`` for a set of input rasters. If all of the "
"input rasters have a non-zero value for a pixel, that pixel will be set "
"to ``1`` in the output raster. If any of the input rasters have ``0`` "
"values for the pixel it will be set to ``0`` in the output raster."
msgstr ""

